# 🌌 Fusion Realm: Anime Combat Blueprint Website

![Fusion Realm Banner](https://example.com/your-banner-image.jpg)

Welcome to the official website source for **Fusion Realm**, a premium mobile game blueprint that fuses anime combat mechanics, scroll upgrades, boss zones, fusion tiers, and a complete clan war system – all built for Unity or Godot studios. 🎮🔥

---

## 📦 What's Inside This Website Package?

- **index.html** – Responsive, modern site (dark theme)
- **Autoplay Trailer Support** – Add your `trailer.mp4`
- **Custom Background** – Swap out `bg.jpg` with your design
- **SEO Optimized** – Ready for Google discovery
- **Ko-fi Support** – Monetize with fan donations
- **README.md** – All usage instructions & licensing

---

## 💡 Key Sections of the Website

- 🏠 **Homepage** – Welcome + tagline
- 🎥 **Live Trailer** – Embed your gameplay
- 📖 **Game Lore & Mechanics** – Clan wars, scroll upgrades, fusion lab, emotion system
- 🚀 **Call to Action** – “Buy Blueprint” button (GitHub or Gumroad)
- ☕ **Support Developer** – Ko-fi donation embedded

---

## 🧪 How to Replace Video and Background

1. Rename your gameplay trailer to `trailer.mp4` and place it in the same folder.
2. Rename your background image to `bg.jpg` or change the file name in `index.html`.

---

## 🌍 SEO Meta Tags (Already Included)

- Title: Fusion Realm - Anime Combat Game Blueprint
- Keywords: Anime fusion game, Unity mobile blueprint, Scroll upgrades, Fusion mechanics, Godot game system
- Description: A complete anime-style combat game system with tier evolution, clan wars, and scroll fusion built for indie game devs.

